default, the leads that have status &#8220;Customer&#8221; will be excluded because they are converted to a customer and no longer needed to be seen in the table on table load if you want to list them you will need to apply the filters.<\/p>\n<div class=\"st-alert st-alert- \">Make sure you don&#8217;t rename\u00a0the default system <a href=\"https:\/\/help.perfexcrm.com\/lead-statuses\/\">status<\/a> Customer to something else to avoid confusions.<\/div>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Convert Lead to a Customer Click on the lead and wait for the modal to be opened, on the top button click Convert to a customer. The convert to customer modal will be shown and the system will try to auto-populate some fields like first name, last name.. If custom fields found for lead will [&hellip;]<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":0,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"footnotes":""},"categories":[14],"tags":[],"class_list":["post-461","post","type-post","status-publish","format-standard","hentry","category-leads"],"aioseo_notices":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/help.perfexcrm.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/461","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/help.perfexcrm.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/help.perfexcrm.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/help.perfexcrm.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/1"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/help.perfexcrm.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=461"}],"version-history":[{"count":0,"href":"https:\/\/help.perfexcrm.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/461\/revisions"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/help.perfexcrm.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=461"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/help.perfexcrm.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/categories?post=461"},{"taxonomy":"post_tag","emb